M

main(String[]) - Static method in class com.MainClass
This method is main executable method of this class steps: 1- create an object of GraphWalkerClient 2- create an object of DigiKalaTestClass 3 -call has next service and while graph has next node or edge do: 3-1- call next service to get name of next method 3-2- invoke method of DigiKalaTestClass class by name 3-3- call get data service and print data 4- call getStatistics service and print json type of result
MainClass - Class in com
This class implements simple Digikala Model-based testing
